```py
SELECT ROUND(SUM(chp02.proportional_sum(ST_Transform(a.geom,3734), b.geom, b.pop))) AS population 
  FROM nc_walkzone AS a, census_viewpolygon as b
  WHERE ST_Intersects(ST_Transform(a.geom, 3734), b.geom)
  GROUP BY a.id;
```
